rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm... I'm glad that Vandham...
No, that Vandham-san found me.

rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0002
rows.name:
If I had gone to Acedia,
I think I'd be dead.

rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0003
rows.name:
That Marveni guy was a totally
untrustworthy adult, wasn't he?

rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Vandham-san was always straightforward
and easy to understand...

rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I finally get it now. That old guy
was an adult you could trust.

rows.label: tlk41100141_05_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm grateful to be here. To
Vandham-san, and to you guys, too.
